{
  "stem": "6736.2",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "It was absolutely not SS.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "They pulled out the Jews with the shuls and literally ripped their beards.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "They were shaving the beards and they were laughing, making fun.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And they ripped the beards.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "And it made a terrible impact on me.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "But again, we were hoping that, uh, they're going to be defeated, because England and France already declared war.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "But I saw the brutality of the Germans.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "Later, in the-- every time came out new laws.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "First, we couldn't walk on the sidewalks.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "We had to walk on the street.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "Then they tell us that when you're over 13 years old, or 12, you had to wear a armband, a white armband with the Jewish star.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And in December, when the first snow fell on Krakow, they circled around the Kazimierz, all the streets, because all where the Jewish people live.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "And they were screaming and yelling.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "And it, it strike me they were saying schmutzigen, that's 'dirty Jews.' Schmutzigen.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "Yet they went into the houses.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "And most people in my building were poor people.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "My mother had a little ring, a few silver candlesticks, no fur, no nothing.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "And they will take away everything.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "And they will put it together on the courtyard.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "As I told you, they put tables on the courtyard.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "And they will, right then and there, make packages and send away to their mothers or girlfriends, or-- and to me, they looked like a bunch of robbers.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 47,
      "text": "And they were so organized that for those people who they took away a lot of stuff, they gave them little pieces of paper that, uh, when the war ends, they will give it back.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 48,
      "text": "But they need the fur for the [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 49,
      "text": "And they need this and they need that.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
